This extension will help you with bad UX of the eaukcija.sud.rs with fetching the data of the articles and showing them into the popup without having to leave the page.
Since the website doesn't remember chosen category from the left menu or pagination and always returns you to the home page when going back, this extension solves that problem so you can check the articles without having to click on them.
